@startuml
autonumber

participant "Your Code" as App
participant "SSEChatConsoleAdapter" as Adapter
participant "dc.http.FastHTTP" as FastHTTP
participant "API (OpenAI)" as API

App -> Adapter: GetStream()
Adapter --> App: Returns `stream` object

note over App
  Prepares JSON body
  (with "stream": true)
end note

App -> FastHTTP: DirectPost(url, body, .client, stream)
FastHTTP -> API: HTTP POST Request

note right of FastHTTP: Stream Mode activated

loop For each SSE (Server-Sent Event)
    API --> FastHTTP: Data chunk (text/event-stream)
    FastHTTP -> Adapter: Transmits chunk to `stream`
    note over Adapter
      Prints content
      to console
    end note
end

API --> FastHTTP: End of connection
FastHTTP --> App: Returns final response

@enduml